### Recommendations for DC Consulting Practice

| # | Recommendation | Priority |
|---|---------------|----------|
| 1 | **AI Infrastructure Specialization** — Liquid cooling, high-density power distribution, GPU facility planning | 🔴 Critical |
| 2 | **Financial Modeling Proficiency** — Excel DCF, TCO, IRR using Section 6 frameworks | 🔴 Critical |
| 3 | **India Market Focus** — Target Mumbai, Chennai, Hyderabad, Bangalore hyperscaler projects | 🟠 High |
| 4 | **Sustainability & ESG Advisory** — LEED/BREEAM, PUE consulting, carbon reporting | 🟠 High |
| 5 | **Ecosystem Positioning** — Study Equinix's interconnection model for tenant mix advisory | 🟡 Medium |
| 6 | **Risk-Adjusted Project Evaluation** — Power availability = first step of every site feasibility | 🔴 Critical |

